\"description\" : \"SmallRye BeanBag SISU integrates the SmallRye BeanBag programmatic bean container with Eclipse SISU metadata and annotations. It scans SISU and Plexus component resources from class loaders and registers the discovered beans with a BeanBag builder.\",\nmetadata/org.codehaus.plexus/plexus-archiver/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Plexus Archiver is a Java component for creating and extracting archive formats such as ZIP, TAR, JAR, and related compressed variants. It provides archiver and unarchiver abstractions used by Plexus and Maven tooling to add files, directories, resources, permissions, and metadata to archives.\",\nmetadata/org.codehaus.plexus/plexus-archiver/index.json:23:    \"description\" : \"Plexus Archiver is a Java component for creating and extracting archive formats such as ZIP, TAR, JAR, and related compressed variants. It provides archiver and unarchiver abstractions used by Plexus and Maven tooling to add files, directories, resources, permissions, and metadata to archives.\",\nmetadata/plexus/plexus-utils/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Plexus Utils provides common Java utility classes historically used by Maven and Plexus-based projects. It includes helpers for file and IO handling, string manipulation, command-line execution, directory scanning, graph processing, introspection, and XML utilities.\",\nmetadata/plexus/plexus-utils/index.json:24:    \"description\" : \"Plexus Utils provides common Java utility classes historically used by Maven and Plexus-based projects. It includes helpers for file and IO handling, string manipulation, command-line execution, directory scanning, graph processing, reflection and introspection, and XML utilities.\",\nmetadata/plexus/plexus-utils/index.json:38:    \"description\" : \"Plexus Utils provides common Java utilities historically used by Apache Maven and Plexus-based projects. It includes helpers for file and IO handling, string manipulation, command-line execution, DAG processing, introspection, and XML utilities.\",\nmetadata/org.apache.maven.plugins/maven-compiler-plugin/3.10.0/reachability-metadata.json:19:      \"type\": \"org.apache.maven.execution.DefaultMavenExecutionRequest\",\nmetadata/org.apache.maven.plugins/maven-compiler-plugin/3.8.1/reachability-metadata.json:19:      \"type\": \"org.apache.maven.execution.DefaultMavenExecutionRequest\",\nmetadata/org.apache.maven.plugins/maven-compiler-plugin/3.9.0/reachability-metadata.json:19:      \"type\": \"org.apache.maven.execution.DefaultMavenExecutionRequest\",\nmetadata/org.apache.maven.plugins/maven-compiler-plugin/3.11.0/reachability-metadata.json:38:      \"glob\" : \"META-INF/maven/org.apache.maven/maven-core/pom.properties\"\nmetadata/io.github.x-stream/mxparser/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"MXParser is a small XML pull parser implementation forked from xpp3_min 1.1.7 with changes merged from the Plexus fork. It provides the parser portion of the XML Pull API for Java applications that need lightweight streaming XML parsing.\",\nmetadata/org.apache.maven/maven-core/2.0.6/reachability-metadata.json:51:      \"glob\": \"META-INF/maven/org.apache.maven/maven-core/pom.properties\"\nmetadata/org.apache.maven/maven-core/index.json:5:    \"source-code-url\" : \"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/org/apache/maven/maven-core/$version$/maven-core-$version$-sources.jar\",\nmetadata/org.apache.maven/maven-core/index.json:7:    \"test-code-url\" : \"https://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/maven/components/tags/maven-$version$/maven-core/src/test\",\nmetadata/org.apache.maven/maven-core/index.json:8:    \"documentation-url\" : \"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/org/apache/maven/maven-core/$version$/maven-core-$version$-javadoc.jar\",\nmetadata/org.apache.maven/maven-archiver/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Maven Archiver provides utilities for Maven plugins and builds to create JARs and other archive files from a Maven project. It handles archive configuration such as manifests